    <subfield code="a">A simple approximate easy-to-use analytic formula is suggested for the absolute integrated-over-angle energy spectrum of neutrons from a high- <math altimg="si0003.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mrow><mi>Z</mi></mrow></math> spallation neutron target driven by 500–1500 MeV proton beams. Overall, the formula is probably reliable to within a factor ~2–3, and could be useful for quickly making rough ‘back of the envelope’ estimates.</subfield>
